---
import MiFoto from "../../assets/img/MiFoto.png";
---

<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row"
>
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={MiFoto.src}
      alt="Photo of Pol"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Pol</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I am a <span class="text-primary font-semibold">resilient</span> video-game design and development student with a strong passion for
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">problem-solving</span>, structured work, and constant learning. I thrive on
      iterating and refining my work to deliver the best possible result.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I enjoy working in collaborative, <span class="text-primary font-semibold">team-based environments</span>, where I can
      contribute, learn from others, and grow together. I consider myself
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">intuitive</span> and <span class="text-primary font-semibold">creatively restless</span>: always seeking the most appropriate
      solution for the project, balancing innovation with practicality.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      In short: I'm a motivated, <span class="text-primary font-semibold">versatile developer</span> ready to contribute
      technically, creatively, and socially to a game-dev team, while staying
      open to learning and improving constantly.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
